{"word":"ἐνίσσω","slug":"ἐνίσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνίσσω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:collateral'>collat.</a> form of <a href='S:ἐνίπτω'><el>ἐνίπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to attack, reproach</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; epic <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἐνισσέμεν</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐνισσόμενος</el> <i>misused</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}